### getString() {#a3168618a19701d0fb78aefb4d4e664de}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="StringRef llvm::AsmToken::getString () const"
  labels = {["inline"]}>
Get the string for the current token, this includes all characters (for example, the quotes on strings) in the token.

The returned <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a> points into the source manager&#39;s memory buffer, and is safe to store across calls to Lex().
